'''Baltic Air Surveillance Network''' ('''BALTNET''') is an [[air defense]] [[radar]] network operated by the [[Baltic States]] of [[Latvia]], [[Lithuania]] and [[Estonia]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mil.ee/index_eng.php?s=baltnet |title=Archived copy |access-date=2017-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080603222803/http://mil.ee/index_eng.php?s=baltnet |archive-date=2008-06-03 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref>

