The '''Krzyż za Zasługi dla ZHP''' ("[[Cross of Merit (Poland)|Cross of Merit]] for the ZHP") is the highest decoration of the [[Polish Scouting and Guiding Association]] (ZHP). The order is awarded to members of the ZHP for heroic acts. It was established on 1 July 1965. The Order has three classes:

